<output language="Java">
<p>
A Java interface with getters and setters for the attributes defined in the component definition.  It will 
extend the interface specified by the "extends" attribute.
</p>
<p>
After all data objects have been processed, classifications are applied to all JPA entities and data objects.
</p>
</output>

